MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Build the detail in the TSNAP_INV_DTL table for Invoice & Harvest IDs in the current snapshot
MAPPING.NAME: m_Snap_Inv_Dtl

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT t1.snap_id ,t1.req_run_ts create_ts ,d.inv_id ,d.HVST_ID ,d.period_id ,d.inv_stat_cd ,d.SNAP_STAT_CD FROM VRAP.tsnap t1 -- new snapshot ,VRAP.tsnap t2 -- current snapshot ,VRAP.TSNAP_INV_DTL D -- invoice snapshot detail WHERE T1.SNAP_RUN_sTAT_CD = 2 --(RUNNING) AND t1.period_id = t2.period_id AND t1.model_typ_cd = t2.MODEL_TYP_CD AND t1.RUN_MODE_CD = t2.RUN_MODE_CD AND t2.SNAP_SEQ_NB = -1 -- restrict to current snaps only AND t2.snap_id = d.SNAP_ID AND d.SNAP_STAT_CD = 1 -- restrict to only good/active inv/harvests from the current snapshot ORDER BY substr(t1.period_id,1,1) ,substr(t1.period_id,4,2) ,substr(t1.period_id,2,2) WITH UR
